gottengeography (1.2.1-precise2ubuntu1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  [ Robert Bruce Park ]
  * Use GSettings instead of GConf. Closes #41.
  * Bring the test suite up to speed with the recent GSettings migration.
  * Update translation instructions.
  * Improve filesystem correctness.
  * Drop package_data from setup.py.
  * Workaround for https://bugs.launchpad.net/intltool/+bug/381347
  * Expand test coverage of drag&drop.
  * Extend distutils to record installation prefix at build time.
  * Persist window size in GSettings.
  * Honor zoom level when linking to Google Maps.
  * Switch position of maps link and map source button.
  * Give up on ChamplainMapSourceFactory as per Jiri's suggestion.
  * Streamline ActorController.display, because it's called frequently.
  * Correct Cycle Map max zoom level.
  * Issue #12: First draft of an application icon.

  [ Marc Ordinas i Llopis ]
  * Added gir1.2-glib-2.0 to dependencies.

